<title>USA: WONDERWARE SETTLES SUIT, TO TAKE CHARGE.</title>
<headline>WONDERWARE SETTLES SUIT, TO TAKE CHARGE.</headline>
<dateline>IRVINE, Calif. 1997-08-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Wonderware Corp reached an out of court settlement and ended all disputes with two former employees of the company.</p>
<p>Although terms of the settlement were not disclosed, Wonderware said itwill settle all claims for cash, resulting in a one-time charge of approximately $1.9 million, including attorney's fees and related costs, which will be taken during the third quarter of this year.</p>
<p>In the third quarter of last year, Wonderware reported a loss of $0.15 a share or $1,990,140.</p>
